OL,6,FA driver, who police say 'ignored'
OL,7,Fbridge closure signs for the M48
OL,8,FSevern Bridge had their car battered
OL,9,Fby heavy winds.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police responded to
OL,12,Fthe incident on the evening of
OL,13,FThursday 28 March.
OL,15,FOn X, formerly Twitter, the force's
OL,16,Froad's policing unit said the driver
OL,17,Fwas caught out by a heavy gust.
