OL,6,FIt added: "National Highways closed
OL,7,Fthe M48 bridge due to high winds,
OL,8,Fhowever this driver decided to ignore
OL,9,Fthe signs.
OL,11,F"This action not only put their life
OL,12,Fin danger but also those of the
OL,13,Fresponding emergency services.
OL,15,F"It's closed for a reason!"
OL,17,FThe bridge was shut for several hours,
OL,18,Fbut reopened at around 2am on Friday
OL,19,F29 March.
